snippet: Crimson Tide running back Derrick Henry finished with a career-high 236 yards and two scores, and the defense came up with a team-record three interceptions that were returned for touchdowns in a win over the Aggies.
abstract: College Football Top 25 Roundup; Louisiana State defeats Florida, 35-28; other college football scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Crimson Tide running back Derrick Henry finished with a career-high 236 yards and two scores, and the defense came up with a team-record three interceptions that were returned for touchdowns in a win over the Aggies.
